0lies%20in%20the%20foothills%20between%20Manipur's%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Ukhrul%20and%20Imphal%20East%20districts.%20It%20will%20remain%20a%20remarkable%20day%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20small%20team%20comprising%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20a%20producer%2C%20farmers%2C%20an%20army%20Captain%20and%20some%20soldiers%2C%20who%20successfully%20transplanted%20a%205.5-feet-tall%2C%20fruit-bearing%20hog%20plum%20tree%2C%20locally%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eheining%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20amid%20the%20intermittent%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMud%20is%20a%201.25%20hectare-large%20concept%20village%20near%20Manipur's%20%26quot%3Bliving%20museum%26quot%3B%20at%20Sekta%2C%2023%20km%20from%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%20Tree%20and%20bamboo%20plantations%20are%20prioritised%20activities%20here%20since%202020.%20The%20place%20serves%20as%20a%20landscaping%20exercise%20to%20run%20an%20environmentally%20friendly%20village%20and%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20community%20interactive%20centre%2C%20a%20family%20outdoor%20activity%20spot%2C%20a%20space%20for%20specialised%20residential%20training%20programmes%20and%20a%20meditation%20centre.%20All%20these%20are%20essentially%20for%20self-exploration%20and%20understanding%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20digging%20a%20water-harvesting%20pond%20the%20size%20of%20half%20a%20football%20field%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20focus%20has%20so%20far%20been%20on%20planting%20fruit-bearing%20and%20indigenous%20trees%20and%20local%20bamboo%20species.%20Apart%20from%20a%20long%20list%20of%20prized%20possession%20-%20olive%2C%20guava%2C%20gooseberry%2C%20mango%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20wild%20apple%2C%20papaya%2C%20pear%2C%20star%20fruit%20and%20Arjun%20tree%20(Arjuna%20Myrobalan)%20-%20Mud%20village%20is%20now%20home%20to%20the%205.5-feet-tall%20hog%20plum%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20picturesque%20Manipur%2C%20the%20charm%20of%20Mud%20village%20is%20the%20surrounding%20hill%20ranges%20offering%20outdoor%20adventure%20activities%20like%20trekking%20and%20camping.%20Another%20attraction%20is%20the%20remnant%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20atop%20Chanung%20hill%2C%20just%20above%20the%20village.%20Trenches%20and%20bunkers%20built%20by%20the%20Japanese%20Army%20on%20the%20ridges%20of%20Chanung%20during%20their%20siege%20of%20Imphal%20still%20exist%2C%20more%20or%20less%20in%20the%20shape%20and%20size%20they%20were%20built%20in%201944.%20The%20allied%20forces%20used%20to%20call%20these%20fortifications%20%26quot%3Bpimples%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20recorded%20in%20the%20war%20history%20that%20the%20Japanese%20siege%20of%20Imphal%20failed%20as%20the%20allied%20forces%20kept%20supply%20lines%20intact%20with%20air%20drops.%20This%20strategy%20helped%20the%20Allies%20win%20the%20Imphal%20and%20Kohima%20battles%20and%20made%20the%20Japanese%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20all%20this%20history%20now%2C%20and%20what%20is%20so%20extraordinary%20about%20a%20hog%20plum%20tree%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224pivepag%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F4pivepag_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turbulent%20times%20that%20Manipur%20has%20been%20living%20in%20since%20May%203%20is%20extraordinary.%20The%20consequences%20and%20the%20after-effects%20of%20the%20'peace%20rally'%20called%20by%20the%20All%20Tribal%20Students'%20Union%20of%20Manipur%20(ATSUM)%20are%20unprecedented.%20The%20provocation%20for%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20drew%20the%20fault%20line%20between%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20is%20astounding.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20communal%20violence%20seen%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20is%20horrendous.%20The%20way%20social%20media%20is%20manipulated%20to%20push%20narratives%20is%20distasteful.%20The%20way%20most%20in%20the%20national%20media%20and%20celebrity%20talk-show%20hosts%20buying%20the%20narratives%20without%20any%20fact-checking%20is%20even%20more%20indigestible.%20Hence%2C%20the%20extraordinariness%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfathomable%20violence%20of%20burning%20down%20houses%2C%20looting%20properties%20and%20targeting%20people%20and%20villages%20have%20become%20the%20very%20basis%20for%20a%20sweeping%20narrative%20that%20separation%20is%20the%20only%20solution.%20This%20call%20came%20from%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%2C%20the%20two%20hill%20districts%20dominated%20by%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribe.%20They%20have%20held%20on%20to%20the%20narrative%20that%20their%20community%20is%20under%20attack%20and%20they%20have%20been%20chased%20away%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20just%20as%20the%20Meiteis%20who%20were%20living%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tengnoupal%20have%20been%20evacuated%20and%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20want%20a%20separate%20political%20administration%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20or%20specifically%2C%20the%20Meiteis.%20There%20is%20little%20scope%20for%20a%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20this%20narrative%20emerged%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20violence%20broke%20out.%20For%20a%20state%20that%20has%20seen%20much%20ethnic%20violence%20-%20the%20Kuki-Naga%20bloodbath%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20the%20Kuki-Paite%20clash%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20and%20the%20Meitei-Muslim%20clash%20-%20Manipur%20has%20never%20had%20a%20narrative%20about%20separate%20administration%20or%20autonomy.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20reconciliation%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20naturally%2C%20for%20a%20multi-ethnic%20civilization%20living%20in%20harmony%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20with%20written%20records%20dating%20back%20to%202000%20years%20since%2033%20AD%2C%20meddling%20with%20its%20territorial%20and%20political%20integrity%20seemed%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22agv4goho%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fagv4goho_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_12_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20chronologically%20seen%2C%20trouble%20started%20in%20Churachandpur%20with%20the%20burning%20of%20a%20forest%20department%20office%20before%20the%20'tribal%20solidarity%20peace%20rally'%20began%2C%20in%20which%20insurgents%20in%20camouflage%20battle%20dress%20armed%20with%20AK-56%20rifles%20were%20clearly%20seen%20participating.%20Subsequently%2C%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20homes%20and%20shops%20of%20unarmed%20Meiteis%20in%20Bishnupur%20district%20bordering%20Churachandpur%20and%20in%20the%20international%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh%20started%20coming.%20SOS%20calls%20by%20the%20trapped%20Meiteis%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20after%20which%20even%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20services%20from%20May%203%20evening%20could%20not%20prevent%20the%20retaliatory%20attacks%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20people%20who%20made%20Imphal%20their%20home%20had%20to%20flee%20for%20safety%20to%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%20as%20they%20had%20become%20the%20targets%20of%20the%20Meitei%20rage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20violence%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20central%20forces%2C%20the%20dark%20smoke%20gradually%20subsided%20in%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts.%20However%2C%20sporadic%20gunfights%20continued%20in%20the%20foothills%20where%20the%20valley%20ends%20and%20the%20hills%20start%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20bordering%20Kuki-Chin-Zo%20dominated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20gunfights%20between%20people%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20armed%20with%20weapons%20looted%20from%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20armoury%2C%20licenced%20rifles%2C%20country-made%20weapons%20and%20those%20imported%20from%20Myanmar%20came%20out%20from%20Sugnu%20and%20Serou%20between%20Kakching%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20Chandel%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20Phayeng-Senjam%20Chirang%20between%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20Khamenlok%2C%20which%20borders%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20story%20of%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree%2C%20Mud%20village%20is%205%20km%20away%20from%20the%20two%20troubled%20areas%20of%20Chanung%20and%20Khamenlok.%20Other%20than%20taking%20the%20inter-village%20roads%2C%20both%20areas%20can%20be%20reached%20by%20hiking%20up%20the%20Tombakhong%20hill%20range%20to%20reach%20Chanung%20and%20then%20trek%20further%20up%20south%20to%20reach%20Khamenlok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20areas%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20attacks%20and%20counterattacks%20between%20the%20warring%20factions.%20Villagers%20here%20are%20compelled%20to%20keep%20watch%20with%20their%20licenced%20guns%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20are%20supported%20by%20well-armed%20volunteers%20on%20both%20sides.%20There%20is%20a%20palpating%20sense%20of%20perpetual%20threat%20and%20the%20first%20to%20launch%20the%20offensive%20naturally%20gets%20the%20better%20of%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ocnoegqo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Focnoegqo_manipur-violence-_625x300_05_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20began%2C%20a%20residential%20school%20built%20to%20international%20standards%20was%20inaugurated%20at%20Chanung.%20This%20school%20was%20the%20target%20of%20arson%20by%20well-armed%20Kukis%2C%20who%20climbed%20down%20the%20hill%20ranges%20from%20Khamenlok.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20prompt%20response%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20foiled%20the%20attack%20in%20May-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20incident%20exposed%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20Chanung%2C%20Loushangkhong%20and%20Sekta%20areas%20to%20Kuki%20attacks.%20Villagers%20in%20Chanung%20and%20Lo