tvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fhd3f02qo_manipur-violence-_625x300_05_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20how%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree%20was%20transplanted%20at%20Mud%20village%20on%20June%2011%2C%20with%20two%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20participating.%20This%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20moment%20-%20people%20transplanting%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20ethnic%20clash.%20In%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20areas%20between%20Mud%20village%20and%20Khamenlok%20saw%20the%20biggest%20single-day%20fatalities%20and%20maximum%20burning%20down%20of%20homes%20since%20violence%20started%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2012%2C%20the%20Kuki%20villages%20of%20Khopibung%2C%20Khamenlok%2C%20Chullouphai%20and%20Aigejang%20were%20destroyed%20by%20armed%20Meitei%20village%20volunteers.%20Some%20of%20them%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20at%20Aigejang%20church.%20In%20the%20counterattack%2C%20well-armed%20Kuki%20forces%20reportedly%20fired%20rocket-propelled%20grenades%20at%20the%20church%2C%20killing%20the%20nine%20Meiteis%2C%20leaving%20four%20missing%20and%20nine%20others%20injured.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Meitei%20volunteers%20went%20on%20to%20burn%20down%20nine%20more%20Kuki%20villages%20in%20Khamenlok.%20On%20June%2028%2C%20reports%20of%20landmines%20around%20Khamenlok%20came%2C%20after%20which%20the%20army%20and%20state%20forces%20went%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20defuse%20the%20mines.%20The%20combine%20forces%2C%20however%2C%20detected%20numerous%20well-armed%20Kuki%20insurgents%20dressed%20in%20black.%20Such%20was%20the%20scale%20of%20violence%20seen%20at%20Khamenlok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20countermeasures%20of%20the%20combined%20forces%20have%20stepped%20up.%20These%20measures%20have%20succeeded%20in%20recovering%20looted%20guns%2C%20ammunition%20and%20bombs.%20Altogether%2C%201%2C100%20guns%2C%2013%2C700%20bullets%20and%20250%20bombs%20have%20been%20recovered%20so%20far.%20The%20combined%20f