n%20a%20new%20market%2C%20according%20to%20a%20review%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20sites%20by%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20has%20long%20battled%20bots%20and%20juiced%20engagement%20on%20the%20app.%20The%20platform%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-deleting-fake-likes-follows-third-party-apps-2018-11%5C%22%3Edeleting%20fake%20followers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20likes%20for%20years%2C%20and%20Instagram%20even%20has%20a%20section%20about%20this%20behavior%20in%20its%20community%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHelp%20us%20stay%20spam-free%20by%20not%20artificially%20collecting%20likes%2C%20followers%2C%20or%20shares%2C%20posting%20repetitive%20comments%20or%20content%2C%20or%20repeatedly%20contacting%20people%20for%20commercial%20purposes%20without%20their%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20Instagram's%20community%20guidelines%20page%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screengrab%20of%20different%20prices%20for%20fake%20followers%20on%20Threads%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64af124b94be880019f3ad73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFameSavy%20is%20one%20of%20many%20services%20offering%20packages%20for%20followers%20on%20Threads.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%2FFameSavy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20influencer-marketing%20platform%20HypeAuditor%2C%20on%20average%2C%20about%2013.8%25%20of%20influencers'%20Instagram%20followers%20are%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B%20accounts.%20HypeAuditor%20defines%20suspicious%20accounts%20as%20any%20Instagram%20page%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20bots%20or%20%26quot%3Buse%20specific%20services%20for%20likes%2C%20comments%2C%20and%20followers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20follower%20count%20metric%20still%20holds%20some%20weight%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20s