20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cself-aggrandizing%20exercise%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cobfuscate%20ground%20realities%20of%20our%20times%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20artists%2C%20academics%20and%20concerned%20persons%20who%20expressed%20support%20for%20Luis%20said%20that%20dismissing%20a%20museum%20employee%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20made%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity%20%E2%80%9Cpoints%20to%20a%20high-handed%20way%20of%20functioning%20that%20does%20not%20recognize%20the%20constitutionally%20enshrined%20right%20to%20free%20speech.%20The%20artworld%20requires%20critically%20informed%20voices%20to%20be%20given%20the%20space%20to%20express%20concerns%20that%20will%20shape%20its%20future%20in%20a%20constructive%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%2C%20artists%2C%20academics%20and%20other%20concerned%20individuals%2C%20have%20come%20to%20know%20that%20Dr%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%2C%20Manager%2C%20Curatorial%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Publications%20at%20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art%20(KNMA)%2C%20has%20arbitrarily%20been%20terminated%20from%20work.%20The%20action%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20Facebook%20post%20he%20made%20on%2015th%20May%202023%20which%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20museum%20Ms.%20Kiran%20Nadar%20in%20her%20individual%20capacity%2C%20for%20supporting%20and%20publicly%20endorsing%20a%20series%20of%20propaganda%20events%20of%20the%20current%20government%20of%20India%20being%20showcased%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20(NGMA)%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Facebook%20post%20was%20also%20published%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkafila.online%2F2023%2F05%2F17%2Fdecoding-jan-shakti-at-national-gallery-of-modern-art-there-is-no-schindlers-list-sandip-k-luis%2F%5C%22%3EDecoding%20Jan%20Shakti%20at%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20-there%20is%20no%20Schindler%E2%80%99s%20List!%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20condemn%20Sandip%E2%80%99s%20termination%20from%20employment%20and%20demand%20his%20immediate%20reinstatement%20by%20KNMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequent%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20an%20exhibition%20in%20May%202023%2C%20titled%20Jana%20Shakti%20(a%20celebration%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20radio%20propaganda%20Mann%20ki%20baat)%20curated%20by%20Alka%20Pande%2C%20supported%20by%20Ms.%20Nadar%20as%20the%20Advisor%2C%20a%20number%20of%20articles%20appeared%20in%20the%20press%20and%20on%20social%20media%20that%20called%20out%20art%20world%20luminaries%2C%20for%20participating%20in%20what%20was%20obviously%20a%20self-aggrandizing%20exercise%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20The%20exhibition%20in%20effect%20had%20instrumentalized%20artists%20and%20artworks%20to%20obfuscate%20ground%20realities%20of%20our%20times.%20Sandip%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20an%20academic%2C%20contributed%20to%20this%20discussion%20through%20his%20social%20media%20post%2C%20not%20as%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20museum%2C%20but%20as%20a%20thinking%20individual%20who%20recognized%20the%20systems%20of%20domination%20and%20exploitation%20that%20marked%20the%20emerging%20order%20of%20private%20wealth%20and%20its%20role%20in%20constructing%20false%20narratives%20of%20art%20and%20politics%20around.%20In%20response%2C%20he%20was%20served%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshow%20cause%E2%80%9D%20notice%20and%20then%20subsequently%20terminated%20from%20employment%20in%20a%20highly%20opaque%20manner%20by%20the%20museum%20where%20he%20was%20employed%3B%20a%20museum%20that%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Nadar%20Foundation%2C%20the%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20arm%20of%20HCL%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20odd%20that%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20KNMA%2C%20a%20museum%20renowned%20for%20its%20collection%20of%20critically%20acclaimed%20art%20works%20and%20curated%20shows%2C%20was%20not%20able%20to%20accept%20criticism%20of%20her%20own%20shortcomings.%20Mrs.%20Nadar%E2%80%99s%20support%20of%20a%20regressive%20propagandist%20event%20seems%20to%20indicate%20her%20inability%20to%20understand%20the%20critical%20function%20of%20art%20in%20the%20present%20political%20climate%2C%20and%20her%20lack%20of%20subject%20expertise%20to%20shape%20art%20exhibitions%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20cultural%20capital%20accrued%20by%20Mrs%20Nadar%20is%20the%20result%20of%20hard%20work%20put%20in%20by%20many%20individuals%20who%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%20of%20the%20institution%20that%20carries%20her%20name%2C%20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art.%20They%20bring%20to%20bear%20their%20academic%20training%20in%20identifying%20important%20strands%20of%20thinking%2C%20significance%20of%20artworks%20and%20advise%20her%20on%20how%20to%20build%20a%20historically%20relevant%20art%20collection.%20Curation%20requires%20depth%20of%20knowledge%2C%20theorizing%20and%20narrativizing%20for%20public%20access%20and%20knowledge%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20when%20we%E2%80%99re%20locked%20in%20a%20crisis%20where%20government%20run%20cultural%20institutions%20have%20become%20instruments%20of%20state%20sponsored%20propaganda%20rather%20than%20spaces%20for%20critical%20thinking%2C%20it%20becomes%20even%20more%20important%20that%20those%20who%20have%20the%20power%20to%20support%20a%20thriving%20artworld%2C%20understand%20its%20transformative%20power%20rather%20than%20seeing%20art%20as%20just%20another%20aspect%20of%20conducting%20business%20as%20usual.%20We%20therefore%20expect%20even%20private%20museums%20to%20function%20as%20forms%20of%20public%20good%20rather%20than%20personal%20fiefdoms%20of%20the%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20dismiss%20a%20museum%20employee%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20made%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity%20points%20to%20a%20high-handed%20way%20of%20functioning%20that%20does%20not%20recognize%20the%20constitutionally%20enshrined%20right%20to%20free%20speech.%20The%20artworld%20requires%20critically%20informed%20voices%20to%20be%20given%20the%20space%20to%20express%20concerns%20that%20will%20shape%20its%20future%20in%20a%20constructive%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20we%20undersigned%20demand%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20Dr%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20on%20the%20post%20that%20he%20held%20before%20(Manager%2C%20Curatorial%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Publications)%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F658855165%2FSupport-to-Sandip-K-Luis%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Support%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3ESupport%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F658855165%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-E7nesgMQkYQYEjguk4cD%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%221.3323485967503692%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Support%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689259194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13200338%2Fnationalherald-2023-07-9e99d458-36b8-484c-a4e4-b3b64e139299-FwE1jJ0X0AAeUwj.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkiran-nadar-slammed-firing-museum-employee-facebook%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20had%20criticised%20Kiran%20Nadar%20for%20endorsing%20a%20series%20of%20events%20held%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%2C%20which%20critics%20say%20is%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bobfuscate%20ground%20realities%20of%20our%20times%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkiran-nadar-slammed-firing-museum-employee-facebook%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kosovo%3A%20Drink%20thrown%20as%20brawl%20breaks%20out%20in%20Kosovo%20parliament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689259055000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F15083%2Fproduction%2F_130374168_p0g0qsvs.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66193089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20opposition%20lawmaker%20douses%20PM%20Albin%20Kurti%20during%20a%20parliamentary%20debate%20sparking%20a%20brief%20fight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-europe-66193089%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Era%20Of%20Equality%3A%20ICC%20Announces%20Equal%20Prize%20Money%20For%20Men's%2C%20Women's%20Events%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men's%20and%20women's%20teams%20at%20ICC%20events%20while%20also%20making%20changes%20to%20the%20over-rate%20sanctions%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20the%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20in%20Durban%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20ensures%20the%20ICC%20Board%20fulfilled%20its%20commitment%20to%20reaching%20prize%20money%20equity%20by%202030%20well%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20will%20now%20receive%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20the%20equivalent%20finishing%20position%20at%20comparable%20events%20as%20well%20as%20the%20same%20amount%20for%20winning%20a%20match%20at%20those%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20from%20the%20next%20cycle%20will%20award%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20to%20men's%20and%20women's%20champions%20and%20runners-up%20teams%20at%20its%20global%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20our%20sport%20and%20I%20am%20delighted%20that%20men's%20and%20women's%20cricketers%20competing%20at%20ICC%20global%20events%20will%20now%20be%20rewarded%20equally.%20Since%202017%20we%20have%20increased%20prize%20money%20at%20women's%20events%20every%20year%20with%20a%20clear%20focus%20on%20reaching%20equal%20prize%20money%20and%20from%20here%20on%20in%2C%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20will%20carry%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20as%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20same%20for%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20U19s%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Chair%20Greg%20Barclay%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20ICC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26amp%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20that%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20gender%20parity%20%26amp%3B%20inclusivity%20has%20been%20undertaken.%20The%20prize%20money%20at%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICC%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ICC%3C%2Fa%3E%20events%20will%20be%20same%20for%20men%20%26amp%3B%20women.%20Together%20we%20grow....%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jay%20Shah%20(%40JayShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayShah%2Fstatus%2F1679494208569364480%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCricket%20is%20genuinely%20a%20sport%20for%20all%20and%20this%20decision%20from%20the%20ICC%20Board%20reinforces%20that%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20celebrate%20and%20value%20every%20single%20player's%20contribution%20to%20the%20game%20equally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Board%20also%20confirmed%20the%20largest%20ever%20investment%20into%20the%20sport%20after%20the%20distribution%20model%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years%20was%20agreed%20upon.%20Every%20ICC%20Member%20will%20receive%20significantly%20enhanced%20funding%20with%20a%20strategic%20investment%20fund%20ring-fenced%20to%20drive%20global%20growth%20initiatives%20in%20line%20with%20the%20ICC%20Global%20Growth%20Strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20champions%20and%20runners-up%20of%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202020%20and%202023%20won%20USD%201%20million%20and%20USD%20500%2C000%2C%20respectively%2C%20a%20fivefold%20increase%20over%20the%20sum%20awarded%20in%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20statement%20further%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prize%20money%20for%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202022%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20USD%203.5%20million%2C%20up%20from%20USD%202%20million%20for%20winning%20the%202017%20edition%20in%20England%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20aded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Executives'%20Committee%20has%20approved%20changes%20to%20Test%20cricket's%20over-rate%20fines%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20necessity%20of%20preserving%20over-rates%20and%20providing%20equitable%20compensation%20for%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20which%20will%20take%20effect%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20World%20Test%20Championship%20cycle%2C%20players%20will%20be%20fined%205%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20match%20fee%20for%20each%20over%20that%20falls%20short%2C%20with%20a%20maximum%20penalty%20of%2050%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20if%20a%20side%20is%20bowled%20out%20before%20reaching%20the%2080-over%20mark%20and%20the%20new%20ball%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20delivered%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20over-rate%20penalty%20enforced%2C%20regardless%20of%20any%20prospective%20delays.%20This%20amendment%20replaces%20the%20previous%20requirement%20of%2060%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20has%20injected%20renewed%20energy%20into%20Test%20cricket%20giving%20it%20compelling%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20Committee%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement%20released%20by%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20edition%20we%20only%20had%2012%20draws%20in%2069%20matches%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20trend%20continues%20whilst%20we're%20giving%20fans%20the%20best%20value%20for%20money%20and%20keeping%20over-rates%20up.%20The%20Men's%20Cricket%20Committee%20felt%20strongly%20that%20over-rate%20penalties%20in%20the%20form%20of%20WTC%20points%20deductions%20should%20remain%20but%20recommended%20that%20players%20should%20not%20have%20100%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20match%20fee%20at%20risk.%20We%20believe%20this%20provides%20a%20balance%20between%20maintaining%20over-rates%20and%20ensuring%20we%20are%20not%20deterring%20players%20from%20playing%20Test%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689259020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fb5l2qsl8_smriti-mandhana-afp_625x300_22_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men's%20and%20women's%20teams%20at%20ICC%20events%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taylor%20Swift's%20impact%20on%20the%20economy%20has%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20Fed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20performs%20onstage%20during%20the%20Eras%20Tour%20at%20Lincoln%20Financial%20Field%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64aff2ccc22d1a00194540df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Swift%20performs%20onstage%20during%20the%20Eras%20Tour%20at%20Lincoln%20Financial%20Field%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023%20in%20Philadelphia%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Lake%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20stunning%20success%20of%20Taylor%20Swift's%20Eras%20tour%20has%20had%20a%20noticeable%20impact%20on%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20of%20Swift's%20three%20Philadelphia%20concerts%20in%20its%20most%20recent%20beige%20book.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHotel%20revenues%20in%20the%20city%20surged%20to%20their%20highest%20level%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20thanks%20to%20Swift.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20Eras%20tour%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20131%20concerts%20across%2017%20states%20and%205%20continents%2C%20has%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20due%20to%20its%20noticeable%20impact%20on%20local%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tour%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-taylor-swift-fans-spend-concerts-eras-tour-2023-7%5C%22%3Ehas%20attracted%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20fans%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20has%20helped%20boost%20hotel%20revenues%20considerably%2C%20especially%20in%20Philadelphia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20the%20slowing%20recovery%20in%20tourism%20in%20the%20region%20overall%2C%20one%20contact%20highlighted%20that%20May%20was%20the%20strongest%20month%20for%20hotel%20revenue%20in%20Philadelphia%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20in%20large%20part%20due%20to%20an%20influx%20of%20guests%20for%20the%20Taylor%20Swift%20concerts%20in%20the%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Fed%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fmonetarypolicy%2Fbeigebook202307.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20most%20recent%20Beige%20Book.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20performed%20three%20concerts%20at%20Lincoln%20Financial%20Field%20on%20May%2012%2C%2013%2C%20and%2014%2C%20and%20she%20returned%20to%20Pennsylvania%20in%20mid-June%20to%20perform%20in%20Pittsburgh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20Booking.com%2C%20hotel%20prices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-taylor-swift-fans-spend-concerts-eras-tour-2023-7%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20tripled%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20tour%20in%20some%20cities%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20in%20Pittsburgh%2C%20Minneapolis%2C%20and%20Kansas%20City.%20The%20hotel%20occupancy%20rate%20in%20Allegheny%20County%2C%20which%20includes%20Pittsburgh%2C%20approached%20100%25%20during%20the%20Swift%20tour%20and%20hotel%20reservation%20platforms%20crashed%20due%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20web%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20weekend%2C%20Swift's%20tour%20is%20set%20to%20hit%20Denver%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcommonsenseinstituteco.org%2Fswiftonomics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20estimate%20from%20the%20Common%20Sense%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20the%20concert%20will%20generate%20%24140%20million%20for%20the%20state's%20gross%20domestic%20product.%20The%20city%20expects%20about%2075%2C000%20Swift%20fans%20to%20attend%20each%20of%20the%20two%20sold-out%20concerts%2C%20and%20the%20report%20said%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20in%20direct%20consumer%20spending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20truly%20understand%20the%20scale%20of%20Swift's%20upcoming%20Denver%20concerts%20this%20weekend%2C%20the%20report%20highlighted%20that%20the%20two%20Eras%20shows%20will%20generate%20an%20estimated%20%2438%20million%20in%20ticket%20sales%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%2063%25%20of%20the%20famed%20Red%20Rock's%20venues'%20total%20ticket%20sales%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20totality%20of%20Taylor%20Swifts'%20U.S.%20tour%20could%20generate%20%244.6%20billion%20in%20total%20consumer%20spending%2C%20larger%20than%20the%20GDP%20of%2035%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Common%20Sense%20Institute%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20the%20economy%20manages%20to%20avoid%20a%20recession%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-ceos-saying-recession-2023-economy-layoffs-hiring-freezes-2022-10%5C%22%3Ethat%20so%20many%20are%20worried%20about%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20US%20may%20have%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20her%20deeply%20loyal%20fans%20partly%20to%20thank.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swifts-economic-impact-catches-attention-federal-reserve-hotel-revenue-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689258772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64609762d391de0019bdce83%3Fformat%3