ignature%20parental%20rights%20in%20education%20law%20that%20critics%20deemed%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Say%20Gay.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-disney-wont-sue-over-desantis-smearing-its-brand-2023-6%3Futm_source%3Dreddit.com%5C%22%3EAs%20Insider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20DeSantis%2C%20during%20a%20speech%20in%20Orlando%2C%20accused%20the%20entertainment%20giant%20of%20sexualiz%5Bing%5D%20children.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20wrong%20to%20sexualize%20children%2C%20it's%20wrong%20to%20put%20it%20in%20your%20programming%2C%20and%20it's%20wrong%20to%20try%20to%20force%20that%20in%20our%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Florida%20governor%20said%20in%20the%20city%20that%20is%20home%20to%20Disney%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20DeSantis%20spokesperson%20Bryan%20Griffin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20further%20comment%20is%20needed.%20The%20governor's%20statements%20to%20date%20are%20our%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-sues-gov-ron-desantis-alleges-weaponizing-government-power-florida-2023-4%5C%22%3EDisney%20has%20responded%20by%20suing%20the%20governor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20arguing%20that%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20run%20roughshod%20over%20their%20First%20Amendment%20rights.%20Before%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Iger%20had%20pushed%20for%20a%20cooling%20of%20tensions%2C%20although%20such%20a%20detente%20appears%20extremely%20unlikely%20now.%20Disney%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20that%20Iger%2C%20who%20came%20out%20of%20retirement%20to%20return%20to%20his%20old%20job%20leading%20the%20company%2C%20would%20stay%20on%20as%20CEO%20through%202026.%20DeSantis'%20second%20term%2C%20should%20he%20not%20win%20the%20presidency%2C%20would%20end%20roughly%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20This%20means%20the%20two%20biggest%20figures%20in%20the%20fight%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger%20took%20partic