nt%20which%20is%20made%20to%20the%20online%20gaming%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20that%20sense%20it%20is%20not%20retrospective%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20gaming%20companies%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20paying%20tax%20at%20lower%20rates%20on%20Gross%20Gaming%20Revenue%20(GGR)%20which%20works%20out%20to%20be%20less%20than%205%20per%20cent%20which%20is%20applicable%20on%20food%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20Council%20in%20its%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20decided%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20the%20turnover%20of%20online%20gaming%20companies%2C%20horse%20racing%20and%20casinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20rate%20was%20decided%20based%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20group%20of%20ministers%20that%20looked%20at%20taxing%20casinos%2C%20horse%20racing%20and%20online%20gaming.%20The%20issue%20before%20the%20GoM%20(group%20of%20ministers)%20was%20whether%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20GST%20on%20the%20face%20value%20of%20bets%2C%20or%20gross%20gaming%20revenue%2C%20or%20just%20on%20platform%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GST%20Council%20decided%20to%20impose%20tax%20on%20the%20entire%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20on%20online%20gaming%20companies%20would%20be%20imposed%20without%20making%20any%20differentiation%20based%20on%20whether%20the%20games%20required%20skill%20or%20were%20based%20on%20chance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689255060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7ko6i7hc_new-parliament-ani-new-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fclarificatory-amendment-to-gst-act-on-online-gaming-in-parliament-monsoon-session