0Indian%20Air%20Force%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20military%20contingent%2C%20are%20poised%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20flypast%20over%20the%20Champs%20Elysees%2C%20Paris%2C%20where%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20be%20the%20chief%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20look%20of%20the%20Rafales%20was%20revealed%20on%20Thursday%20in%20visuals%20from%20the%20Evreux-Fauville%20Air%20Base%20in%20France.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20First%20look%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20Rafales%20that%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%20on%20July%2014%20in%20Paris%2C%20France%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVisuals%20from%20%C3%89vreux-Fauville%20Air%20Base.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fp1itfkeRaB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fp1itfkeRaB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1679426241324265474%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Abhishek%20Tripathi%2C%20Commanding%20Officer%20of%20101%20Squadron%20(Rafale)%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20formation%20that%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20Flypast%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20for%20us%20that%20we%20have%20brought%20Rafale%20to%20France%20once%20again.%20The%20PM%20will%20be%20the%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20at%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%20and%20we%20will%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20opening%20formations%20of%20the%20Flypast...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20Tripathi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20(Rafales)%20has%20the%20best%20of%20the%20avionics%20which%20all%20the%20fighters%20in%20the%20world%20have%2C%20even%20better%20than%20them...To%20summarise%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20compact%2C%20extraordinary%2C%20powerful%2C%20extremely%20agile%20and%20very%20discreet%20machine...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Anindo%20Sur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20prestigious%20for%20us%20to%20fly%20so%20far%2C%20close%20to%204500%20miles.%20Our%20aircraft%20did%20not%20land%20anywhere%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20we%20did%20air-to-air%20refuelling.%20We%20flew%20continuously%20for%20over%2010%20hours%20-%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20any%20aircraft%20has%20flown%20so%20long%20from%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Group%20Caption%20said%20it%20is%20an%20amazing%20feeling%20for%20India.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20two%20practice%20sorties%2C%20tomorrow%20is%20the%20D-Day%20for%20us...We%20have%20four%20aircraft%2C%20all%20four%20of%20which%20will%20fly...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Rafale%20jets%20that%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20flypast%20over%20the%20Champs%20Elysees%2C%20Paris%2C%20reached%20France%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20traditional%20military%20parade%20is%20held%20annually%20in%20Paris%20during%20Bastille%20Day%20on%20July%2014.%20PM%20Modi%2C%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20France%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20will%20be%20the%20Guest%20of%20Honour%20on%20France's%20National%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20visit%20will%20coincide%20with%20the%2025th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20partnership%26quot%3B%20between%20France%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESquadron%20Leader%20Sindhu%20Reddy%20said%20it%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20tremendous%20pride%20for%20India%20since%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20be%20representing%20our%20country%20as%20well%20as%20our%20Force%20on%20foreign%20land%20in%20front%20of%20our%20PM%20who%20will%20be%20witnessing%20the%20parade...I%20will%20be%20commanding%20the%20Air%20Force's%20contingent%20which%20comprises%2077%20personnel%20of%20which%2068%20will%20be%20marching...%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20Ambassador%20to%20France%20Jawed%20Ashraf%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20Indian%20Rafale%20jets%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20flypast%20over%20the%20Champs%20Elysees%2C%20Paris%2C%20will%20send%20a%20message%20across%20the%20world%20that%20India-France%20ties%20are%20very%20strong%20and%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interaction%20with%20ANI%2C%20Ashraf%20said%20that%20the%20flypast%20and%20marching%20by%20the%20IAF%20air%20warriors%20on%20Bastille%20Day%20follow%20a%20long%20association%20that%20the%20two%20nations%20share%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20field%20of%20air%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20envoy%20also%20termed%20Rafale%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20flypast%20as%20%26quot%3Bvery%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20ship%20could%20have%20come%20from%20India.%20We%20have%20many%20ships.%20What%20is%20important%20is%20that%20both%20our%20soldiers%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20inter-operability%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20trust%20and%20in%20this%20way%2C%20this%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20the%20whole%20world%20that%20the%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20France%20is%20very%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshraf%20also%20underlined%20that%20the%20India-France%20partnership%20is%20about%20the%20power%20of%20values.%20%26quot%3BThe%20military%20relations%20that%20we%20have%20are%20to%20protect%20our%20values%2C%20without%20claiming%20or%20suppressing%20anyone%20else.%20We%20call%20it%20Prime%20Minister's%20partnership%20of%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20France's%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Emmanuel%20Lenain%20tweeted%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20warm%20welcome%20to%20France%20for%20the%20Indian%20Rafale%20jets%20that%20will%20soar%20in%20the%20skies%20of%20Pa