sation)%20in%20favour%20of%20M%2Fo%20I%26amp%3BB%20authorising%20it%20to%20operate%20relevant%20budget%20heads%20in%20their%20demand%20to%20settle%20bills%20raised%20on%20account%20of%20their%20advertisement%20and%20publicity%20campaign%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20amount%20mentioned%20in%20LoA%20(details%20attached).%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20amount%20allocated%20through%20LoA%20will%20not%20be%20available%20for%20expenditure%2Fre-appropriation%20by%20the%20functional%20Ministry%2FDepartment%20in%20the%20current%20FY%202023-24.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CBC%E2%80%99s%20Budget%20for%202023-24%20approved%20by%20Parliament%20is%20Rs%20200%20crore.%20With%20the%20May%2019th%2C%202023%20order%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20the%20Budget%20for%20CBC%20for%20the%20current%20year%20will%20suddenly%20zoom%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%20750%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EParliament%20votes%20Budgets%20for%20all%20Departments%20and%20Ministries%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Each%20programme%2Fscheme%20has%20a%20distinct%20Budget%20Head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20on%20May%2019%2C%202023%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20has%20ordered%20that%2040%25%20of%20the%20funds%20voted%20by%20Parliament%20for%20%E2%80%98Advertising%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYusTFtx52R%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYusTFtx52R%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1679355833711296513%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20money%20will%20be%20used%20by%20the%20CBC%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202024%20general%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20CBC%2C%20along%20with%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20the%20spearhead%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%202024%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsking%20if%20this%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ede%20facto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20misappropriation%E2%80%9D%20of%20funds%2C%20Ramesh%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20prime%20minister%20by%20calling%20him%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPrachar%20Mantri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(broadcasting%20minister).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20propaganda%20machine%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20funds.%20Now%20with%20this%20surgical%20strike%2C%20just%20like%20the%2040%25%20Commission%20Sarkara%20dislodged%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20Modi%20Govt.%20usurps%2040%25%20of%20funds%20already%20allocated%20to%20ministries%20by%20Parliament%20and%20enriches%20the%20CBC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20order%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20subversion%20of%20Parliament%E2%80%99s%20Constitutional%20obligations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20undermined%20the%20expertise%20of%20specific%20ministries%20as%20well%20as%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20budget%20voted%20by%20the%20Parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20I%26amp%3BB%20minister%20Manish%20Tewari%20called%20the%20order%20%E2%80%9Chilarious%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%C2%A0%20%40MIB_India%20by%20an%20executive%20order%20get%20spending%20rights%20on%2040%25%20of%20publicity%20budgets%20appropriated%20by%20Parliament%20under%20separate%20line%20items%20specific%20to%20each%20Ministry.%20This%20is%20totally%20illegal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tewari%20said%20in%20a%20tweet%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20abused%20in%20an%20election%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20hilarious.%20How%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMIB_India%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MIB_India%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20an%20executive%20order%20get%20spending%20rights%20on%2040%25%20of%20publicity%20budgets%20appropriated%20by%20Parliament%20under%20separate%20line%20items%20specific%20to%20each%20Ministry.%20This%20is%20totally%20illegal.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20obvious%20that%20government%20publicity%20funds%20would%20be%20abused%20for%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqfDGn8vEJz%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqfDGn8vEJz%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Manish%20Tewari%20(%40ManishTewari)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FManishTewari%2Fstatus%2F1679386090950774784%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%E2%80%99%20national%20spokesperson%20Pawan%20Khera%20referred%20to%20the%20order%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPawankhera%2Fstatus%2F1679357948827512833%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20promotion%2C%20by%20promotion%2C%20government%20of%20promotion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20in%20the%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20economic%20affairs%20department%2C%20the%20order%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Cmisinterpreted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20official%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20named%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20office%20memorandum%20(OM)%20itself%20is%20self-explanatory%20and%20is%20being%20misrepresented.%3C%