s%20also%20helped%20markets%20settle%20in%20the%20positive%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-share%20BSE%20Sensex%20jumped%20670.31%20points%20or%201.02%20per%20cent%20to%20hit%20its%20all-time%20intra-day%20peak%20of%2066%2C064.21.%20The%20barometer%20settled%20164.99%20points%20or%200.25%20per%20cent%20higher%20at%2065%2C558.89.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSE%20Nifty%20went%20up%20by%2029.45%20points%20or%200.15%20per%20cent%20to%20close%20at%2019%2C413.75.%20During%20the%20day%2C%20it%20rallied%20182.7%20points%20or%200.94%20per%20cent%20to%20reach%20its%20lifetime%20high%20of%2019%2C567.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20domestic%20rally%20was%20supported%20by%20the%20contra%20bet%20buying%20of%20the%20IT%20stocks%20which%20was%20supported%20by%20stable%20margins%2C%20new%20generation%20business%20opportunities%20and%20increase%20in%20pricing%20power%20due%20to%20moderation%20in%20USD%2C%20as%20latest%20US%20inflation%20is%20fast%20approaching%20the%20Fed's%20target%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinod%20Nair%2C%20Head%20of%20Research%20at%20Geojit%20Financial%20Services%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20Sensex%20pack%2C%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%2C%20Infosys%2C%20Bajaj%20Finserv%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20Wipro%20and%20Bajaj%20Finance%20were%20among%20the%20major%20gainers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETCS%20climbed%202.47%20per%20cent%20a%20day%20after%20announcing%20its%20June%20quarter%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20largest%20IT%20services%20company%20on%20Wednesday%20reported%20a%2016.83%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20June%20quarter%20net%20profit%20to%20Rs%2011%2C074%20crore%20but%20sounded%20circumspect%20about%20growth%20prospects%20for%20the%20fiscal%20due%20to%20market%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPower%20Grid%2C%20Maruti%2C%20NTPC%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%2C%20Hindustan%20Unilever%20and%20Nestle%20were%20among%20the%20laggards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20data%20released%20on%