C%20Ashwin%20stole%20the%20limelight%20with%20the%20ball.%20His%20five-wicket%20haul%20made%20him%20the%20third%20Indian%20bowler%20to%20claim%20700%20International%20wickets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20how%20adapting%20to%20the%20pitch%20conditions%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20the%20game.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThought%20it%20was%20a%20pretty%20good%20performance.%20There%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20moisture%20on%20the%20pitch%20earlier%20but%20it%20started%20to%20spin%20later.%20Saw%20on%20the%20TV%20as%20well%20that%20it%20turned%20more%20later.%20Had%20to%20adapt%20early.%20It%20was%20a%20bit%20dry%2C%20have%20to%20get%20the%20pace%20right%20to%20trouble%20the%20batsmen.%20International%20cricket%20is%20all%20about%20adapting%20to%20different%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20signed%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20coming%20to%20the%20match%2C%20West%20Indies%20bundled%20out%20on%20a%20score%20of%20150.%20In%20reply%20to%20the%20hosts'%20total%2C%20India's%20openers%20started%20the%20innings%20on%20a%20positive%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20couple%20of%20early%20LBW%20shouts%20against%20Rohit%2C%20India's%20opening%20stand%20didn't%20face%20issues%20in%20the%20third%20session.%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20took%20his%20time%20to%20open%20his%20account%2C%20but%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20adjusted%20himself%20to%20the%20pitch%20conditions%20he%20started%20to%20take%20on%20the%20bowlers%20with%20confidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20opened%20his%20account%20with%20a%20beautifully%20executed%20shot%20to%20find%20the%20fence%20for%20a%20four.%20He%20tried%20to%20find%20the%20boundary%20once%20again%20with%20another%20shot%20but%20the%20fielder%20denied%20him%20to%20claim%20back-to-back%20boundaries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20looked%20confident%20with%20his%20shot%20selection%20and%20defensive%20approach%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20th