n%20or%20leave%20Sachin%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20lovers%20have%20found%20each%20other%2C%20the%20history%20of%20their%20respective%20nations%20is%20bitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20both%20nuclear-armed%20nations%2C%20have%20fought%20three%20wars%20since%20being%20carved%20out%20of%20the%20subcontinent%20in%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20expelled%20the%20other's%20high%20commissioner%20in%202019%2C%20and%20bilateral%20diplomatic%2C%20cultural%2C%20business%20and%20sporting%20links%20are%20very%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20police%20insist%20that%20Seema's%20long-term%20stay%20will%20be%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20grant%20me%20citizenship%26quot%3B%2C%20Seema%20pleaded%2C%20a%20red%20headscarf%20covering%20her%20hair%20and%20her%20four%20young%20children%20playing%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Destined'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApostasy%20is%20considered%20punishable%20by%20death%20in%20some%20interpretations%20of%20Islam.%20Seema%20said%20she%20had%20already%20received%20online%20threats%20and%20insisted%20the%20couple%20would%20%26quot%3Blive%20and%20die%20together%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema's%20proclamation%20of%20%26quot%3Bundying%20love%26quot%3B%20for%20Sachin%20and%20a%20promise%20to%20only%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20dead%20woman%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20featured%20on%20a%20raucous%20Indian%20TV%20debate%20this%20week%20drew%20cheers%20from%20the%20crowds%20sitting%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20said%20she%20had%20been%20first%20attracted%20by%20Sachin's%20gaming%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20the%20couple%20met%20in%20person%20in%20March%20in%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20became%20sure%20about%20leaving%20her%20%26quot%3Babusive%26quot%3B%20Pakistani%20husband%20--%20charges%20he%20denies%20--%20after%20the%20first%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20it%20took%20months%20of%20meticulous%20planning%20with%20help%20from%20YouTube%20videos%20on%20how%20to%20enter%20India%20via%20Nepal.%20In%20May%2C%20she%20succeeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20travel%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20with%20God's%20love%2C%20we%20were%20destined%20to%20meet%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin's%20family%20only%20learned%20of%20her%20existence%20when%20he%20rented%20a%20nearby%20apartment%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20some%20resistance%2C%20but%20my%20father%20and%20everyone%20accepted%20us.%20They%20are%20happy%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sachin.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20everything%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20police%20found%20out%20after%20they%20tried%20to%20get%20married%20at%20a%20local%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Still%20my%20family'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema's%20estranged%20husband%2C%20Ghulam%20Haider%2C%20left%20his%20job%20as%20a%20labourer%20and%20rickshaw%20driver%20to%20earn%20more%20money%20for%20his%20family%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaider%2C%20who%20said%20he%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20PUBG%2C%20wants%20his%20family%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20earnestly%20appeal%20to%20Indian%20and%20Pakistani%20authorities%20to%20bring%20my%20wife%20and%20children%20back%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghulam%20Haider%20told%20AFP%20by%20phone%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaider%20said%20the%20couple%2C%20from%20different%20Baloch%20tribes%2C%20have%20a%20defiant%20love%20story%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForbidden%20by%20their%20families%20from%20marrying%2C%20they%20ran%20away%20to%20get%20hitched%20--%20a%20taboo%20in%20Pakistan%20that%20can%20sometimes%20lead%20to%20so-called%20honour%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%2C%20a%20jirga%20(council%20of%20elders)%20was%20summoned%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20one%20million%20rupees%20(around%20%243%2C640)%20was%20slapped%20on%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20far%20from%20my%20home%2C%20from%20my%20family%2C%20and%20it%20is%20very%20agonising%20for%20me%20because%20we%20married%20out%20of%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'She%20is%20an%20adult'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20couple%20have%20received%20a%20popular%20welcome.%20Crowds%20from%20nearby%20villages%20have%20been%20visiting%20them%20since%20their%20arrest%20grabbed%20national%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20selfies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rakesh%20Chand%2C%2037%2C%20who%20drove%20over%20an%20hour%20to%20offer%20his%20congratulations%2C%20one%20of%20the%20dozens%20lining%20up%20to%20greet%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSachin%20is%20very%20happy%2C%20even%20his%20family%20has%20accepted%20them%2C%20so%20the%20government%20must%20ensure%20that%20she%20isn't%20forced%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20the%20streets%20near%20her%20old%20home%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Dhani%20Bakhsh%20village%20in%20eastern%20Karachi%2C%20the%20news%20has%20not%20been%20welcomed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20people%20know%20about%20Seema's%20story%2C%20few%20are%20willing%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20incident%20openly%20--%20though%20they%20gossip%20in%20small%20groups%20on%20street%20corners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20forget%20about%20her%2C%20as%20she%20has%20gone%20and%20she%20is%20an%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Haider's%20cousin%20Zafarullah%20Bugti%2C%20blaming%20PUBG%20for%20turning%20Seema%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20psycho%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeema%20herself%20is%20unrepentant%2C%20calling%20Sachin%20the%20%26quot%3Blove%20of%20her%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20insisting%20she%20will%20dedicate%20herself%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20children%20wi