on%20Cabinet%20has%20reportedly%20cleared%20amendments%20to%20the%20Mines%20and%20Minerals%20(Development%20and%20Regulation)%20Act%2C%201957%2C%20to%20allow%20commercial%20mining%20of%20lithium%20and%20other%20critical%20minerals%20including%20beryllium%2C%20titanium%2C%20niobium%2C%20tantalum%20and%20zirconium.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20private%20companies%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20mine%20these%20minerals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minerals%20in%20question%20are%20key%20to%20the%20production%20of%20mobile%20phones%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20solar%20panels%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20wind%20turbines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20mineral%20blocks%20%5Bof%20these%20critical%20minerals%5D%20will%20be%20auctioned%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20aware%20of%20the%20developments%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Fcabinet-approves-lithium-auction-process%2Farticle67071797.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3Eusinessline%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Funion-cabinet-clears-commercial-mining-of-lithium-5-other-critical-minerals%2F1666679%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20once%20Parliament%20clears%20the%20amendments%2C%20the%20government%20will%20be%20able%20to%20grant%20a%20single%20exploration%20licence%20to%20companies%20through%20such%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20single%20exploration%20licence%20will%20encourage%20more%20private%20investment%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20where%20currently%20private%20presence%20is%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20government%20source%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Flithium-reserve-jammu-kashmir-tests-india%5C%22%3EIndia%20announced%20the%20discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20very%20first%20substantial%20lithium%20deposits%2C%20amounting%20to%205.9%20million%20tonnes%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Reasi%20district.%20Experts%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20then%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20lithium%20find%20is%20good%20news.%20If%20more%20assessments%20reveal%20that%20the%20lithium%20resources%20can%20indeed%20be%20tapped%20into%20and%20used%2C%20it%20will%20prove%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20manufacturing%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20the%20development%20of%20these%20reserves%20will%20need%20to%20be%20conducted%20sustainably%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20equity%20%E2%80%93%20scientists%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20mines%20ministry%20had%20compiled%20the%20first%20ever%20report%20on%20identification%20of%20critical%20minerals%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689232368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124126%2Fbattery-g6f2cb070e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-cabinet-clears-amendments-allowing-for-lithium-mining%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20moment%2C%20private%20companies%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20mine%20these%20critical%20minerals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-cabinet-clears-amendments-allowing-for-lithium-mining%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jailed%20Putin%20critic%20forced%20to%20listen%20to%20presidential%20speech%20for%20more%20than%20100%20days%20in%20a%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689232260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-alexei-navalny-russia_6217284.jpg%3F20230713090945%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalny-jailed-putin-critic-forced-to-listen-to-presidential-speech-for-more-than