itizens%20across%20Pune%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20through%20Yodda%20Care%2C%20and%20expects%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20users%20on%20Enable%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20two%20years%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20at%20least%2040%20emergencies%20successfully%2C%20this%20is%20our%20greatest%20achievement%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tarun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20what%20keeps%20him%20motivated.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20extremely%20gratifying%20to%20be%20able%20to%20cater%20to%20so%20many%20senior%20citizens.%20A%20lot%20of%20time%20people%20tend%20to%20equate%20the%20success%20of%20startups%20with%20money%20but%20other%20than%20money%2C%20if%20you%20are%20able%20to%20change%20the%20fabric%20of%20society%2C%20you%20have%20fulfilled%20the%20purpose%20of%20your%20startup%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1688738262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fyodda-tarun-1688736751.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323097%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pune%E2%80%99s%20Tarun%20Sharma%20runs%20Yodda%20Care%2C%20a%20tech%20startup%20that%20helps%20senior%20citizens%20access%20emergency%20care%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20day-to-day%20help%20in%20managing%20daily%20lives.%20He%20shares%20what%20pushed%20him%20to%20start%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323097%2Fpune-man-starts-yodda-elder-care-startup-for-emergency-help-to-senior-citizens%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%3A%20The%20History%20of%20How%20India%20Began%20One%20of%20Its%20Most%20Significant%20Space%20Journeys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20be%20launching%20it